         <OBJECT_CONTRACT ITEM="1">
            <TITLE>
               <P>Market Engagement for Public Realm Infrastructure Works Framework</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>GCC004539CPU</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="45233252"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="WORKS"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Construction, repair and maintenance of Public Realm schemes that include natural stone high quality surfaces, high quality concrete paving, street furniture, green and blue infrastructure, cycle infrastructure and street lighting.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">130000000</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <TITLE>
                  <P>Public Realm Infrastructure Works - value up to 10 000 000 GBP</P>
               </TITLE>
               <LOT_NO>1</LOT_NO>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="45233252"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKM82"/>
               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>Glasgow.</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Construction, repair and maintenance of public realm schemes that include natural stone high quality surfaces, high quality concrete paving, street furniture, green and blue infrastructure, cycle infrastructure and street lighting. Items included would be as follows:</P>
                  <P>— kerbs, setts, and slabs,</P>
                  <P>— bollards, signage, seating, cycle racks, hostile vehicle mitigation measures,</P>
                  <P>— Water Sensitive Urban Design including Rain Gardens; installation of planting beds as part of any surface water drainage scheme,</P>
                  <P>— Planting Areas; installation of other planting beds as part of public realm works,</P>
                  <P>— Street Trees; to include all underground infrastructure to support tree to maturity,</P>
                  <P>— Street Lighting, both statutory and architectural.</P>
                  <P>Works may also include elements of the following:</P>
                  <P>— Carriageway and Footway Construction and Re-Construction (Bituminous and Concrete),</P>
                  <P>— Carriageway and Footway Resurfacing (Bituminous and Concrete),</P>
                  <P>— Carriageway and Footway Patching (Bituminous and Concrete),</P>
                  <P>— Insitu Recycling,</P>
                  <P>— Drainage (pipes and fittings, ironwork, proprietary ironwork repair systems, catchpits, inspection chamber, culverts, drain cleaning, sump emptying and CCTV surveys),</P>
                  <P>— Earthworks / Remediation,</P>
                  <P>— Site Clearance,</P>
                  <P>— Signing / Lining,</P>
                  <P>— Traffic Management.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="2">
               <TITLE>
